Package: snapShooteR
Title: SNAPSHOOTHER
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: person('Marcelo', 'Alid-Vaccarezza', email = 'maalid@gmail.com', role = c('cre', 'aut'))
Description: A shiny app for take snapshoots from one or two webcams. It allows to label the images and save them in the train-validation-test folder structure.
